Configure Version Control in Microsoft Fabric

---

1ï¸âƒ£ Key Concepts (Must-Know)

What â€œVersion Controlâ€ Means in Fabric

- Uses Git integration (Azure DevOps or GitHub)
- Tracks changes to Fabric items as files in a Git repo
- Enables:
  - Collaboration
  - Change history
  - Rollback
  - Branch-based development (managed outside Fabric)

Golden rule (exam):

Git = source control
Deployment pipelines = environment promotion

